paws 0.1.9

Modify one of your existing presets

Source: R/mediaconvert_operations.R
mediaconvert_update_preset.Rd

Modify one of your existing presets.

mediaconvert_update_preset(Category, Description, Name, Settings)

Arguments

Category

The new category for the preset, if you are changing it.
Description

The new description for the preset, if you are changing it.
Name

[required] The name of the preset you are modifying.
Settings

Settings for preset
